  "original_title": "\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d87\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7\u0ddd\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dba \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0db6\u0db3\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dda\u0dc2\u0dab 04\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "04 researches on the use of asbestos in Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four researches on the use of asbestos in Sri Lanka were presented at the Skills Forum. It was headed by Minister Susil Premajayantha.",
        "The Russian Republic had provided financial support for it and the research was carried out together with the Universities of Colombo and Peradeniya, the National Building Research Organization, and the National Institute of Basic Education.",
        "In addition to the last four reports of those researches, the last report of the action report prepared by the Russian and Sri Lankan delegations was also handed over to the minister.",
        "On this occasion, Ministry Secretary M. N. Mr. Ranasinghe and others joined."
      ],
